<h1>Welcome to a Monster Hunter World Armor and Weapon Database</h1>
<p>This application is a resource for detailed information about weapons, armors, and crafting materials found in Monster Hunter World.</p>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Search:</strong> Easily find specific armors and weapons using the search feature.</li>
  <li><strong>Detailed Information:</strong> Get the stats, crafting requirements, and  abilities of each piece of gear.</li>
  <li><strong>Filter and Sort:</strong> Narrow down your options by filtering.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Getting Started</h2>
<p>Begin by exploring our <a href="/armors">Armor Database</a> or <a href="/weapons">Weapon Database</a>. You can
  search for specific items or use filters to find what you need for your next hunt. Each item's page provides
  detailed information about its attributes and or crafting requirements.</p>

